 lesions in recurrent glucagonoma: A case report and review of literature</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Cristian Ghetie</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2012Jan1 | World Journal of Gastrointestinal Oncology, Vol. 4, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.4251/wjgo.v4.i6.152">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1017/CBO9780511793950.005"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1017/CBO9780511793950.005">Gastrointestinal radiology</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"></ul></div><div class="meta">2011Nov3</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1017/CBO9780511793950.005">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.4158/EP10376.RA"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.4158/EP10376.RA">Pancreatic Endocrine Tumors in Multiple Endocrine Neoplasia Type 1 Syndrome: Review of Literature</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Francesco Tonelli</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Francesco Giudici</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Geri Fratini</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Maria Luisa Brandi</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2011Jul1 | Endocrine Practice, Vol. 17</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.4158/EP10376.RA">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.53347/rID-12907"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="